data.title: RECORD STORE DAY
data.meta_description:
The Genuine Imitation Life Gazette marked a wild, unexpected, utterly satisfying departure for Frankie Valli & The Four Seasons. Inspired by and dropped in the wake of classic psych-pop vocal albums like Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band and Pet Sounds, this is one of the most ambitious efforts from the famed Jersey Boys. Gone are the doo-wop and Motown inspired harmonies, the light pop about girls, and arrived was a complex, insightful album of social commentary. Critics loved it-- it's taken the fans longer to come around. With this beautiful reissue, a new generation can discover a different side of Frankie Valli & The Four Seasons, and go on a wild ride.
Tracklist Side 1 1. AMERICAN CRUCIFIXION 2. MRS. STATELEYS 3. LOOK UP LOOK OVER 4. SOMETHINGS ON HER 5. SATURDAYS FATHER Side 2 1. WALL STREET VILLAGE DAY 2. GENUINE IMITATION LIFE 3. IDAHO 4. WONDER WHAT YOULL BE 5. SOUL OF A WOMAN
